    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "so it's basically just telling me the data is too messy to trust? i'm struggling to explain this in my discussion section without sounding like i'm just making excuses for a weak result. how would you describe that \"messiness\" or the influence of the noise in a more formal, academic way?",
